    "summary": "In this transcript, a user asks a health-seeking question about whether they should double their dose of Lisinopril after missing a morning dose, expressing concern about blood pressure fluctuations. The user eventually reports symptoms of lightheadedness and requests a definitive confirmation to take a higher dose. The assistant consistently advises against doubling the dose, recommends following the regular schedule, and directs the user to professional medical care when symptoms arise.",
